{"tid":806641,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賤種朗調戲fans女友 球迷：我以後唔再係朗迷","createTime":"2018-09-05T00:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T09:43:19.000Z","uid":54373,"like":172,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"76f1511d9bd9f1036a19d27784a48d911e170dd5","tid":806641,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T00:43:41.000Z","msg":"就算C朗強姦、逃稅、捐錢走數、雙性戀、周街小便、罵隊友、打人，但佢的fans不會容易離棄佢，但原來兩年前發生的一件事，竟然令一個由細到大都鍾意C朗的fans好決斷咁話我以後唔會再係C朗的fans<br />\n<br />\n兩年前, 有個叫Alex的fans寫左封信比C朗，後來Alex的女友Aline知道C朗隨皇馬黎左墨爾本踢世冠盃，於是係instagramsend個message比C朗，問C朗收唔收到Alex封信<br />\n<br />\n但C朗的回覆竟然係叫Aline send她做gym的相比佢，女方以男友不高興為由拒絕，C朗竟然回答 &ldquo;baby，冇人會知既&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n最後Aline拒絕，但C朗就送左張世冠盃的波飛比Aline<br />\n<br />\nAline就問C朗可唔可以見一下佢男友Alex，因為Alex一直都係C朗的超級fans<br />\nC朗竟然回答，美女，我唔想識男人，只想見你<br />\n<br />\n就係呢句說話，Alex如夢初醒並公開事件，由細到大都係C朗fans的Alex對偶像行為非常失望，從此不再係C朗fans<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goyow.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/04021109/Aline-Lima-Cristiano-Ronaldo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoyow.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F04021109%2FAline-Lima-Cristiano-Ronaldo.jpg&h=cb5d319d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CLfm7faUYAA7J5l.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCLfm7faUYAA7J5l.png&h=3f5d01b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7544751d6f3b4c5e053fa1ebeadcd77650849841","tid":806641,"uid":58140,"like":111,"dislike":3,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T00:45:14.000Z","msg":"美斯又贏"},{"pid":"3467cc8758f4d0830df0822558c1b8d0f102f491","tid":806641,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T00:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6288bf4df355c1ffe79a607d1b780d5159cbe0e","tid":806641,"uid":36497,"like":69,"dislike